card.desc:
**(Not marked but compulsory to submit):**

A 5-page project plan, including motivation for your project (i.e., why is the work interesting/useful?), suggested methodology (i.e., why is your technical approach sensible/ likely to succeed? ), and a timeline of work, including deliverables, decision points, and risk mitigation.  Your project plan will be formatively assessed by your supervisor and a second independent marker, who will both provide written feedback on your plan.

**Deadline: 24 June**
